item.title: Decoding Messages: The Art of Escort Communication
item.description: Here’s my second-week review at MQPK, and I’m back a bit earlier than I announced because Thursday was my last working day for this week. I’m enjoying the long weekend doing things I love, I always say, “Get a hobby (or hobbies); there are much more fun things to do than just having seggs.‚Äù During the first week, I had the audacity to leave my ad on longer than my work hours, which led to being bombarded by “Are you available?
